1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
Did you know earthquake waves can unlock secrets about our planet?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:09,200
Two main types of seismic waves exist: P waves and S waves.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:11,600
P waves compress and travel faster.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:13,600
They’re the first to arrive.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,400
S waves shear and arrive later, revealing more about the quake's intensity.

6
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:22,400
Detecting these waves helps scientists locate quakes and assess damage.

7
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:25,600
Want to learn more about our planet's mysteries?

8
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,400
Hit subscribe!
